      "description": "Expand the scene to show the procession approaching the imposing, stylized entrance gate of the village, framed by massive traditional banyan trees.",
      "prompt": "Extend the scene to depict the procession moving toward a grand, stylized village gate (cổng làng) with a tiled, curved roof. Include the sprawling, ancient banyan tree (cây đa) with thick, graphic aerial roots hanging down, dominating the upper frame. Maintain the heavy black outlines, flat color fields, and the rustic texture of the Đông Hồ woodcut style."
    },
    {
      "scenario_id": "lotus_pond_crossing",
